{"type":"message","id":"d6d7e6a6","parentId":"f83b0504","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:03:40.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_1UBiCv8os3XnqXtlQQEzr3y0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"plan_id\": \"plan_1773098454_a7c73fd5\",\n  \"original_prompt\": \"Create a comprehensive system analysis report with the following sections:\\n\\n1. **System Inventory**: List all available skills, their status, and dependencies\\n2. **Performance Metrics**: Measure execution time, success rates, and resource usage\\n3. **Integration Map**: Show how skills interact with each other\\n4. **Recommendations**: Prioritized improvements based on findings\\n5. **Executive Summary**: High-level overview for stakeholders\\n\\nRequirements:\\n- Each section should be 300-500 words\\n- Include specific examples and data\\n- Use tables for comparison where appropriate\\n- Reference actual system components\\n- Provide actionable insights\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-03-09T23:20:54Z\",\n  \"estimated_total_tokens\": 69,\n  \"estimated_total_runtime_seconds\": 240,\n  \"global_token_budget\": 16000,\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"task_01\",\n      \"objective\": \"**System Inventory**: List all available skills, their status, and dependencies\",\n      \"description\": \"**System Inventory**: List all available skills, their status, and dependencies\",\n      \"inputs\": [],\n      \"outputs\": [],\n      \"dependencies\": [],\n      \"acceptance_criteria\": [\n        \"Complete the described objective.\",\n        \"Output matches expected format.\"\n      ],\n      \"estimated_tokens\": 19,\n      \"estimated_runtime_seconds\": 60,\n      \"complexity_score\": 0,\n      \"requires_subagent\": false,\n      \"recommended_skill\": null,\n      \"recommended_model\": null,\n      \"priority\": \"low\",\n      \"execution_hints\": {\n        \"parallelizable\": true,\n        \"requires_isolation\": false,\n        \"risk_level\": \"low\