{"type":"message","id":"c1889c27","parentId":"d6d7e6a6","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:03:59.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I can see the problem clearly. The current plan has tasks with abstract objectives like \"**System Inventory**: List all available skills, their status, and dependencies\" but no executable instructions. The tasks are missing the required fields from the mission:\n\n1. `execution_mode`: \"main\" | \"subagent\" | \"mixed\"\n2. `action_type`: \"exec\" | \"python\" | \"skill_invocation\" | \"file_operation\"\n3. `action_instructions`: Specific, executable instructions\n4. `required_inputs`: List of inputs needed\n5. `expected_outputs`: What outputs should be produced\n6. `validation_method`: How to validate task completion\n7. `recommended_skill_or_role`: Which skill/sub-agent should handle this\n8. `artifact_destination`: Where to store outputs\n\nLet me start fixing the code. First, I'll update the `plan_generator.py` to include the new required fields:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yrsP5lRWi6NqlF83VPpbNR0r","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/scripts/plan_generator.py","oldText":"@dataclass\nclass PlanTask:\n    \"\"\"Task representation in a plan.\"\"\"\n    task_id: str\n    objective: str\n    description: str\n    inputs: List[str]\n    outputs: List[str]\n    dependencies: List[str]\n    acceptance_criteria: List[str]\n    estimated_tokens: int\n    estimated_runtime_seconds: int\n    complexity_score: int\n    requires_subagent: bool\n    recommended_skill: Optional[str]\n    recommended_model: Optional[str]\n    priority: TaskPriority = TaskPriority.MEDIUM\n    execution_hints: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None","newText":"@dataclass\nclass PlanTask:\n    \"\"\"Task representation in a plan.\"\"\"\n    task_id: str\n    objective: str\n    description: str\n    execution_mode: str  # \"main\" | \"subagent\" | \"mixed\"\n    action_type: str  # \"exec\" | \"python\" | \"skill_invocation\" | \"file_operation\"\n    action_instructions: str  # Specific, executable instructions\n    required_inputs: List[str]\n    expected_outputs: List[str]\n    dependencies: List[str]\n    validation_method: str  # How to validate task completion\n    estimated_tokens: int\n    estimated_runtime_seconds: int\n    complexity_score: int\n    recommended_skill_or_role: Optional[str]  # Which skill/sub-agent should handle this\n    artifact_destination: Optional[str]  # Where to store outputs\n    priority: TaskPriority = TaskPriority.MEDIUM\n    execution_hints: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":614,"output":641,"cacheRead":32064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33319,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773101020023}}
