{"type":"message","id":"c59735bf","parentId":"f20c1ca5","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:07:45.431Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_maX8i22BFbnIYSRUS8ROFnpT","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n### How Main Agent Uses This Skill:\n1. **Invoke skill** with long/complex prompt\n2. **Receive plan** in JSON format\n3. **Parse and validate** plan structure\n4. **Spawn sub-agents** according to plan recommendations\n5. **Coordinate execution** using dependency graph\n6. **Validate outputs** using acceptance criteria\n7. **Synthesize final result**\n\n### Example Main Agent Workflow:\n```python\n# Main agent detects long prompt\nif should_invoke_long_prompt_orchestrator(prompt):\n    # Invoke skill to get plan\n    plan = invoke_long_prompt_orchestrator_skill(prompt)\n    \n    # Validate plan\n    if validate_plan(plan):\n        # Execute plan\n        executor = PlanExecutor(plan)\n        result = executor.execute_plan()\n        \n        # Synthesize final result\n        final_output = synthesize_result(plan, result)\n        return final_output\n```\n\n## File Layout\n```\nskills/long-prompt-orchestrator/\n  SKILL.md                           (this file)\n  scripts/\n    orchestrate.py                   (main orchestration - generates plans)\n    decompose.py                     (detect & decompose prompts)\n    plan_generator.py                (generate structured plans)\n    todo.py                          (persistent checklist - for reference)\n    token_budget.py                  (token management - for reference)\n    validate.py                      (validation logic - for reference)\n    recovery.py                      (recovery logic - for reference)\n    learning_emit.py                 (incident emission)\n    context_monitor.py               (monitor context size)\n    context_archive.py               (archive reasoning artifacts)\n    semantic_index_builder.py        (build semantic index of artifacts)\n    semantic_context_search.py       (search semantic index)\n    task_state_manager.py            (persist task state across sessions)\n    session_manager.py               (session lifecycle management)\n    memory_router.py                 (dynamic agent memory routing)\n    context_cleanup.py               (orchestrate context cleanup)\n    distributed_orchestrate.py       (enhanced plans with distribution recommendations)\n  references/\n    design.md                        (design decisions)\n    pattern_keys.md                  (Pattern‑Key definitions)\n    DISTRIBUTED_EXECUTION_MODEL.md   (decision framework for distribution)\n    TASK_ASSIGNMENT_POLICY.md        (task assignment guidelines)\n  examples/\n    example_basic.md                 (simple long prompt example)\n    example_complex.md               (complex multi‑file example)\n```\n\n## Plan Format Specification\n\nPlans follow a structured JSON format defined in `PLAN_FORMAT_SPECIFICATION.md`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"plan_id\": \"plan_20260309_1600_a1b2c3d4\",\n  \"original_prompt\": \"truncated prompt...\",\n  \"created_at\": \"2026-03-09T16:00:00Z\",\n  \"estimated_total_tokens\": 12000,\n  \"estimated_total_runtime_seconds\": 300,\n  \"global_token_budget\": 16000,\n  \"tasks\": [\n    {\n      \"task_id\": \"task_01_introduction\",\n      \"objective\": \"Write introduction section\",\n      \"description\": \"Detailed description...\",\n      \"inputs\": [],\n      \"outputs\": [\"introduction.md\"],\n      \"dependencies\": [],\n      \"acceptance_criteria\": [\"File exists\", \"Word count >= 250\"],\n      \"estimated_tokens\": 800,\n      \"estimated_runtime_seconds\": 60,\n      \"complexity_score\": 3,\n      \"requires_subagent\": false,\n      \"recommended_skill\": null,\n      \"recommended_model\": null,\n      \"priority\": \"medium\",\n      \"execution_hints\": {\n        \"parallelizable\": true,\n        \"requires_isolation\": false,\n        \"risk_level\": \"low\",\n        \"retry_policy\": \"immediate_2\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"dependency_graph\": {\n    \"nodes\": [\"task_01_introduction\"],\n    \"edges\": [],\n    \"topological_order\": [\"task_01_introduction\"]\n\n[108 more lines in file. Use offset=200 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773101265424}}
