Skill: salesforce-code-auditor\n\n\n=== Demonstrating Real Artifact Creation ===\nUsing temporary workspace: /tmp/tmp2bm_5d_m\n\nGenerated task instructions:\n# Create file: test_artifact.txt\necho 'File: test_artifact.txt' > test_artifact.txt\necho 'Content for: Create test artifact file' >> test_artifact.txt\n\n✓ Artifact created successfully: /tmp/tmp2bm_5d_m/test_artifact.txt\n  File size: 141 bytes\n  Content preview: Test artifact created by plan execution\nTask: Create test artifact file\nGenerated at: 2026-03-10T00:...\n✓ Validation passed: Check test_artifact.txt exists and is not empty; Validate: File exists with content\n\n\n=== Testing Distributed Execution Capability ===\nPlan ID: plan_1773101647_4e5c92d0\n\nExecution Mode Distribution:\n  subagent: 3 task(s)\n\nDependency Graph Analysis:\n  Nodes: 3\n  Edges: 2\n  Execution Order: ['task_main', 'task_subagent', 'task_synthesis']\n\nTasks that can run in parallel: ['task_main', 'task_subagent']\nThis enables true distributed execution when tasks are assigned to different agents.\n\n================================================================================\nTEST RESULTS SUMMARY\n================================================================================\n✓ Plan format updated from abstract to executable\n✓ Main agent can parse and use new plan format directly\n✓ Real artifacts can be created from plan execution\n✓ Distributed execution enabled when tasks marked for subagents\n✓ All required fields present in new plan format:\n  - execution_mode: main|subagent|mixed\n  - action_type: exec|python|skill_invocation|file_operation\n  - action_instructions: specific, executable instructions\n  - validation_method: how to validate completion\n  - artifact_destination: where to store outputs\n\nEvidence saved to: /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/test_evidence/\n\n✅ SUCCESS: long-prompt-orchestrator now generates executable plans!","cwd":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestam