{"type":"message","id":"f44d3abb","parentId":"67a82e1b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:14:25.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! The test shows that the skill is now generating executable plans. Let me also update the SKILL.md to mention the new executable plan format:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Hrmqg0FzKV1oZIlRAxAZzDtH","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace/skills/long-prompt-orchestrator/SKILL.md","oldText":"## What This Skill Does\n\n**This skill ONLY generates plans.** It does NOT execute tasks or spawn sub‑agents.\n\nWhen given a long/complex prompt, it:\n1. **Detects** if decomposition is needed (token count, multi‑objective, dependencies, etc.)\n2. **Decomposes** the prompt into manageable mini‑tasks\n3. **Generates** a structured execution plan with:\n   - Task definitions with objectives, inputs, outputs, dependencies\n   - Dependency graph for execution order\n   - Resource allocation recommendations\n   - Validation protocol\n4. **Returns** the plan to the main agent for execution\n\nThe main agent then:\n- Parses and validates the plan\n- Spawns sub‑agents according to plan recommendations\n- Coordinates execution using the dependency graph\n- Validates outputs using acceptance criteria\n- Synthesizes the final result","newText":"## What This Skill Does\n\n**This skill ONLY generates executable plans.** It does NOT execute tasks or spawn sub‑agents.\n\nWhen given a long/complex prompt, it:\n1. **Detects** if decomposition is needed (token count, multi‑objective, dependencies, etc.)\n2. **Decomposes** the prompt into manageable mini‑tasks\n3. **Generates** a structured **executable** execution plan with:\n   - Task definitions with **executable instructions** (not abstract objectives)\n   - **Execution mode** (main, subagent, mixed) for each task\n   - **Action type** (exec, python, skill_invocation, file_operation)\n   - **Specific action instructions** that main agent can execute directly\n   - **Validation methods** for task completion\n   - **Artifact destinations** for outputs\n   - Dependency graph for execution order\n   - Resource allocation recommendations\n4. **Returns** the executable plan to the main agent for direct execution\n\nThe main agent can now:\n- **Execute tasks directly** without manual translation\n- **Parse and validate** the executable plan\n- **Spawn sub‑agents** according to execution_mode recommendations\n- **Coordinate execution** using the dependency graph\n- **Validate outputs** using validation_method criteria\n- **Store artifacts** at specified destinations\n- **Synthesize** the final result"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-api-deepseek-com","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":1129,"output":589,"cacheRead":57216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58934,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773101647460}}
